I think we should still begin.

01:17.511 --> 01:20.747
Let's start with the reading of the
minutes from our last meeting. Kelly?

01:26.186 --> 01:27.654
"At the beginning of the last meeting...

01:27.855 --> 01:30.257
...I suggested we have
no more meetings.

01:31.859 --> 01:33.927
It was seconded by Bud, my brother...

01:34.127 --> 01:35.762
...and Dad, my daddy.

01:36.997 --> 01:38.866
We stared dully at Mom
and then were forced...

01:39.066 --> 01:41.468
...into a chorus of
'We Love the Baby.'

01:41.668 --> 01:42.836
Then Mom left to pee...

01:43.036 --> 01:45.639
...and Dad suggested
that we play a gleeful round...

01:45.839 --> 01:47.708
...of 'How Fat is She? '

01:50.444 --> 01:52.846
