01:54.047 --> 01:55.782
We all laughed, and Dad said:

01:55.983 --> 01:57.951
'Don't write this down, Pumpkin."'

01:59.186 --> 02:01.054
That concludes my report.

02:02.589 --> 02:05.225
Let the record show
your father is a weenie.

02:06.493 --> 02:09.062
And now, can we have a report
from the treasury?

02:16.403 --> 02:19.873
