has nothing in his pants.

02:29.216 --> 02:31.485
Oh, my God. Baby meeting!

02:31.885 --> 02:34.288
Get back here, young man!

02:34.688 --> 02:37.591
Yeah, pay your respect to the fetus
just like the rest of us.

02:44.231 --> 02:46.800
Most glorious
inhabitant of the womb...

02:48.335 --> 02:51.004
...please accept the blessing
of this unworthy one.

02:51.205 --> 02:53.607
I love you more than I love myself.

02:53.807 --> 02:55.209
Hail baby.

02:59.580 --> 03:01.315
The baby is pleased.

03:01.515 --> 03:02.683
You may sit.

03:02.883 --> 03:04.785
Listen, I have great news.

03:04.985 --> 03:07.855
As the only intelligent
living male Bundy...

03:08.689 --> 03:10.657
...I'm proud to announce
I've gotten a scholarship...

03:10.858 --> 03:12.359
...and I'm going to junior college.

03:12.759 --> 03:15.395
And just how does that
pertain to the baby?

03:16.096 --> 03:16.930
Thank you.

03:17.231 --> 03:18.866
So I decided to start college
across town...

03:19.199 --> 03:21.168
...instead of this neighbourhood,
where I'm accused...

03:21.368 --> 03:22.936
...of being a total social failure.

03:23.437 --> 03:25.105
Don't be so hard on yourself, Bud.

03:25.305 --> 03:26.473
I'm sure lots of cool guys...

03:26.673 --> 03:28.809
...spend their Friday nights
watching Star Trek reruns...

03:28.976 --> 03:32.045
...hoping to catch a glimpse
of Klingon cleavage.

03:36.216 --> 03:38.952
Let the record show that I was
wetting the screen with my tongue...

03:39.152 --> 03:40.354
...to clean it.

03:45.626 --> 03:47.060
To continue...

03:47.294 --> 03:48.562
Chicks love new blood.

03:48.795 --> 03:50.697
So I'm assuming
a whole new identity.

03:50.898 --> 03:52.866
As of now, my story is
I'm a bad-boy rapper...

03:53.066 --> 03:54.701
...from the streets of New York.

03:56.236 --> 03:57.905
Goodbye, Bud Bundy.

03:58.372 --> 04:00.440
Hello, Grandmaster B.

04:03.277 --> 04:04.711
What does the B stand for?

04:04.912 --> 04:06.280
"Brother of an idiot."

04:10.184 --> 04:11.418
Anyhow, if anyone asks...

04:11.618 --> 04:13.387
...my parents sent me here
to clean up my act...

04:13.587 --> 04:16.490
...because I either killed a guy
or spray-painted a tree or something.

04:16.757 --> 04:20.160
Excuse me, but isn't that the plot
for The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air?

04:20.594 --> 04:22.996
Well, that's an NBC show,
so who would know that?

04:29.269 --> 04:31.839
So if anyone asks,
I'm not related to any of you.

04:32.239 --> 04:34.107
And I'm coolly dangerous.

04:35.876 --> 04:38.011
I am not going
to be dateless this year.

04:38.178 --> 04:40.747
- Now, if you've finished, Bud...
- B.

04:56.463 --> 04:58.599
And just yesterday he was in diapers.

04:59.566 --> 05:00.667
Literally.

05:01.869 --> 05:03.637
I killed a man in New York, you know.

05:03.837 --> 05:06.273
Forgive me, Ghostbuster B.

05:07.641 --> 05:09.409
It's Grandmaster B.

05:09.610 --> 05:10.744
Of course, honey.

05:11.278 --> 05:12.779
Now, let's get back
to the baby meeting.

05:12.980 --> 05:15.048
Given the fact, and I would like
this to go on record...

05:15.249 --> 05:17.017
...that your father earns nothing...

05:17.217 --> 05:19.219
...it seems that we'll be
a little pressed for room...

05:19.419 --> 05:20.921
...when the blessed event comes.

05:21.421 --> 05:22.689
- Hail baby.
- Hail baby.

05:23.824 --> 05:27.394
Who is loved more than all babies
that came before him.

05:27.628 --> 05:29.129
Now, since we have limited space...

05:29.329 --> 05:32.099
...I would like to move that the baby
share a room with Daddy and me.

05:32.299 --> 05:34.301
We'll just put a crib
at the foot of the bed.

05:36.970 --> 05:38.572
I would like the record to show...

05:38.805 --> 05:41.441
...that I would rather sleep
in a bunk bed under Oprah.

05:45.546 --> 05:47.481
I would rather engage
in a frolicking threesome...

05:47.681 --> 05:49.716
...with Roseanne
and her cool husband.

05:52.052 --> 05:54.188
I would rather play naked Twister...

05:54.354 --> 05:56.823
...with every one
of the Golden Girls...

05:57.925 --> 06:01.461
...than have that little screaming
doodie geyser at the foot of my bed.

06:03.163 --> 06:05.465
I've said my piece. Thank you.

06:07.835 --> 06:09.436
Hail baby.

06:10.671 --> 06:12.005
All right then, let's have a vote.

06:12.206 --> 06:15.676
All those in favour of the baby sharing
a room with Mommy and Daddy?

06:15.876 --> 06:18.045
- Opposed?
- I must use my veto power.

06:18.245 --> 06:21.248
- Motion is carried.
- Veto! Veto, I say!

06:21.582 --> 06:24.017
All right, everybody, I'll see you
at the next baby meeting.

06:24.251 --> 06:26.720
But for now, Mommy
must use the bathroom.

06:27.087 --> 06:28.789
Al, if you would be so kind...

06:29.056 --> 06:29.890
