06:30.090 --> 06:31.758
You will not make a mockery
of my veto power.

06:31.959 --> 06:34.428
I am the man of the house,
and my will is law!

06:39.933 --> 06:43.036
For the record,
she's now up to 500 pounds.

06:47.074 --> 06:49.076
This is my temporary crib, babe.

06:52.112 --> 06:53.914
Thanks for carrying my books.

06:55.983 --> 06:57.818
Anything to help keep
your gun hand free...

06:58.018 --> 06:59.386
...Mixmaster B.

07:01.021 --> 07:02.523
That's Grandmaster B.

07:03.123 --> 07:04.525
And I don't carry a gun anymore.

07:04.725 --> 07:06.260
Because I have a new life
here in Bel-Air...

07:06.460 --> 07:08.095
I mean, Chicago.

07:09.596 --> 07:11.331
Have I shown you my scar?

07:12.032 --> 07:14.835
You scare and excite me
when you talk like that.

07:15.736 --> 07:16.837
Take me.

07:18.472 --> 07:20.440
First, do it for me, B.

07:21.542 --> 07:23.043
Give me your rap.

07:24.111 --> 07:25.212
All right.

07:55.776 --> 07:57.177
And now...

07:58.111 --> 07:59.246
You may take me.

07:59.446 --> 08:00.614
Thank you.

08:00.814 --> 08:01.949
No problem.

08:06.553 --> 08:07.988
Well, look.

08:08.622 --> 08:11.758
My little man
is getting his first kiss.

08:14.061 --> 08:16.196
You're the coolest, Grandma B.

08:18.332 --> 08:20.100
That's Grandmaster B.

08:21.101 --> 08:21.902
Look, babe...

08:22.102 --> 08:24.471
...I think I'm going to have to rap
my way out of the rent now.

08:24.671 --> 08:25.973
You go on home
and wait by the phone.

08:26.173 --> 08:29.076
If I call and you're not there,
you go to the bottom of the list.

08:34.914 --> 08:36.582
What did I tell you two?!

08:37.417 --> 08:38.619
I am Grandmaster B.

08:38.818 --> 08:40.554
Grand. Master. B.

08:40.754 --> 08:43.457
Mom, I'm cool. You're
ruining it for me! I'm cool.

08:44.958 --> 08:47.594
Gee, I'm really sorry,
Grand Marshal B.

08:49.196 --> 08:51.832
No, Mom, I think it's Bed-Wetter B.

08:52.666 --> 08:55.169
Are you sure? I thought
it was Court Jester B.

08:56.303 --> 08:57.938
Peg! Peg!

08:58.338 --> 08:59.873
Guess what I found in the attic?

09:00.073 --> 09:02.609
It's something of my father's
that served him well for 20 years.

09:03.043 --> 09:05.712
And now, will serve me
for the rest of my life.

09:05.913 --> 09:07.414
A pair of socks?

09:08.382 --> 09:10.317
Bud, what do you think I found?

09:10.517 --> 09:12.886
If it's a rubber woman, Dad,
I can explain.

09:14.655 --> 09:16.023
You send away
for one Archie comic...

09:16.223 --> 09:18.225
...the next thing you know,
they put you on a list...

09:21.328 --> 09:22.496
Pumpkin?

09:23.163 --> 09:24.865
You found a pumpkin, Daddy?

09:27.100 --> 09:28.435
Well, I guess I'll tell you all...

09:28.635 --> 09:30.938
...since none of you
singly deserve to know.

09:33.040 --> 09:34.441
I found my father's hammer.

09:37.344 --> 09:39.913
This hammer has been
in my family for generations.

09:40.113 --> 09:43.350
With this, my father hit
the now-famous Bundy nail.

09:43.550 --> 09:45.185
And upon that nail,
he did hang his hat.

09:49.423 --> 09:50.891
My dad had one great dream...

09:51.091 --> 09:52.659
...and that dream was handed down...

09:52.860 --> 09:55.062
...from generation to generation
of male Bundys:

09:55.262 --> 09:56.396
To build their own room...

09:56.597 --> 09:58.765
...and live separately from their wives.

10:00.634 --> 10:01.668
Sadly, they all failed.

10:01.869 --> 10:04.271
No, genetically they all failed.

10:04.838 --> 10:06.607
Well, not me! I'm going to do it!

10:07.174 --> 10:09.409
Look, Dad. I've got your hammer.

10:09.610 --> 10:11.912
Your little boy's
gonna build his own room.

10:12.980 --> 10:14.681
Mom, who is he talking to?

10:14.982 --> 10:16.517
Grandpa.

10:16.717 --> 10:17.918
Hi, Grandpa.

10:24.858 --> 10:27.995
Look, Dad, I'm building my own room.

10:29.229 --> 10:31.598
I'll dedicate the first nail to you.

10:36.403 --> 10:37.771
Damn cheap Sheetrock!

10:39.740 --> 10:42.209
I can't believe you're gonna let
that moron move out of your room.

10:42.576 --> 10:45.712
Marcie, you're assuming
he can actually do this.

10:45.913 --> 10:47.047
You know the Bundy legacy:

10:47.247 --> 10:50.651
What they don't finish in 30 seconds,
they never finish.

10:51.785 --> 10:53.487
Besides, you know, it's important...

10:53.687 --> 10:55.556
...to let your man fail
in front of your eyes.

10:55.756 --> 10:57.491
