11:03.197 --> 11:04.698
"It's okay, honey.

11:04.898 --> 11:07.167
I'm sure it happens to all men.

11:08.902 --> 11:12.673
It doesn't mean there's anything
wrong with you, does it?"

11:15.242 --> 11:16.810
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Or when you say:

11:17.010 --> 11:19.146
"It's okay, honey.
You're probably just tired...

11:19.346 --> 11:21.348
...and unsure of your manhood."

11:21.548 --> 11:23.317
