14:43.350 --> 14:44.651
Save me.

14:45.285 --> 14:47.221
All right, but just one night.
And on one condition:

14:47.421 --> 14:49.189
- What?
- It's just you and me...

14:49.389 --> 14:51.458
...and you don't tell
one single guy about this place.

14:51.658 --> 14:52.926
I swear.

14:53.293 --> 14:54.795
Hey, Bobby, throw me that.

14:56.029 --> 14:57.364
Tater storm.

14:59.700 --> 15:01.835
