can play the guitar.

15:33.333 --> 15:34.434
What's wrong with you idiots?

15:34.635 --> 15:37.437
Any second, the women are going
to come pouring through that door.

15:37.671 --> 15:39.840
Don't you know they can sense
a man smiling a mile away?

15:40.040 --> 15:41.408
Al, don't worry about it.

15:41.608 --> 15:44.044
