they wouldn't tell anyone. Right?

15:44.244 --> 15:45.279
- We swear!
- We swear!

15:45.913 --> 15:48.782
And so I move that this room
shall be our clubhouse...

15:49.016 --> 15:51.418
...for our newly formed
ladies group W.O.M. B...

15:51.618 --> 15:55.455
...which stands for
"Women Owe Men Bubkes."

15:56.223 --> 15:58.025
- All in favour?
- Aye!

15:58.225 --> 16:00.127
- Opposed?
- Veto.

16:01.094 --> 16:02.629
Motion carried.

16:03.297 --> 16:06.233
Now, ladies, are there any complaints
that we'd like to share?

16:06.433 --> 16:08.001
I got hemorrhoids.

16:09.069 --> 16:11.205
I've got varicose veins.

16:11.405 --> 16:14.274
Well, I've got an itch
my husband refuses to scratch.

16:16.410 --> 16:17.544
Excuse me...

16:17.778 --> 16:19.813
...where do we go when
we're feeling emotional?

16:21.014 --> 16:22.683
We can use Al's bathroom.

16:25.419 --> 16:28.355
Thou shalt not insult my bowl
with pregnant heinies.

16:31.191 --> 16:32.159
Where are you going, Al?

16:32.359 --> 16:34.528
