16:48.141 --> 16:49.676
Keep the gates open, Dad!

16:49.910 --> 16:51.879
I got a busload coming for you!

16:53.213 --> 16:55.115
Go for it, son.

17:05.959 --> 17:07.761
Well, for this special baby meeting...

17:07.961 --> 17:09.762
...we'd like to welcome Daddy back.

17:09.963 --> 17:12.733
A man who kept his garage up
for five hours.

17:12.933 --> 17:15.669
