17:55.309 --> 17:56.910
Was it in Desert Storm?

17:58.078 --> 18:00.214
Well, I had my own little
Desert Storm, baby...

18:00.414 --> 18:02.015
...in the streets of New York.

18:02.216 --> 18:05.185
